00:05:26.640 --> 00:05:31.840
[Amit Varma]: was not just to talk about the 91 reforms per se, but also the India of the four decades

00:05:31.840 --> 00:05:36.960
[Amit Varma]: before that. Why did we go in the direction we went in? What were the consequences? What

00:05:36.960 --> 00:05:41.920
[Amit Varma]: was life like before 1991? And all three of us are old enough to remember some of that.

